page.title: 01MY DAY - SATURDAY 29TH JUNE
page.content: I woke up at 8.25 a.m. I had a wash and got dressed. I had a breakfast of Bran Flakes and toast. I went round Christopher's and we went for a bike ride around the green. When we got back I had to serve petrol for a little while (because I live in a garage). After that we started to make a go-kart. We looked around for some wood and after a while we found some and made a go-kart, all except for the wheels because we did not have any. We have put a card in the shop window. After that we rode around on our bikes thinking of something else to do. Then we rode home because we had to have tea. I had sausages, chips and peas. After that we went into Attleborough to change some videos. When we got back it was about 7.10 p.m. I watched Cannonball Run 2 and went to bed at 9.45 p.m.
